'''2X-NM''' ('''Tooexx-ennam''') was once a [[Metropolis Razer]] [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]] who was converted to become a cooking droid by [[Mother (suspected smuggler)|Mother]] for his [[space diner]], [[Mother's]]. Although he had his [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] replaced with a spatula and his former programming changed to hold some very tasty recipes, he was known to still be able to wield a mean set of [[Ginsu Knife|Ginsu Knives]] when called on to defend the diner.

